// 2. Added storage keyword to the struct variable acc in Put and Collect functions.
// 3. Replaced call.value with transfer in Collect function to prevent reentrancy vulnerability.
// 4. Removed payable keyword from Collect function as it is not necessary.
// 5. Added require statement in Collect function to check if the balance is sufficient and unlock time has passed.
